title: What.Not.To.Wear s08e24 Julie
description:
WHAT NOT TO WEAR

Two fashion stylists and a team of hair and makeup advisors help revamp the look of individuals who have been nominated by their friends for makeovers due to their lamentable appearance, using a $5,000 budget.

SEASON 8 EPISODE 24 - Julie


Julie is a 32-year-old style writer who's baggy bohemian wardrobe should be kept off the catwalk. After a recent breakup and a lifelong history of body insecurities her wardrobe has become a "cover story." Will Julie be able to close the book on her eccentric ensemble and find a style that both professional and ready for romance? OR will shedding her style shield keep this animal print enthusiast and her growl out of reach?
